column5: Was out on Nippissing last night looking for new fishing grounds. Found a crazy shoal in the middle of the lake. Caught alot of bass and a few nice walleye.
Nice solid looking fish man, good job!   MTBF
hopefully you marked that spot on the gps
Oh you better believe it!  LOL  The coordinates are....      ...you didnt think I'd really tell you did you?    Haha
